parameters:
\CE[94]\N<Holy Knight Captain>You have all worked
hard in this battle!

\N<Holy Knight Captain>Lately, we have been facing
repeated attacks from the Demon Alliance, but this
time we were able to defend ourselves without
suffering significant damage!

\N<Holy Knight Captain>Needless to say, it's all
thanks to everyone's hard work! Although the
attacks will continue, let's first heal our wounds
and prepare for the next battle!

\N<Holy Knight Captain>Amidst such intense
battles, there is someone who has achieved
remarkable results! With the king's approval, this
time we will commend that individual!
\N<Jazz>Now, Rain, before the king!
\OC[31]\N<Rain>Hah!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>A holy knight, Rain, has
arrived.

\N<King>Rain. I hear that even though you have
recently become a holy knight, you are running
around the battlefield and displaying the strength
equivalent to that of a hundred people.

\N<King>The contribution to this victory is
immeasurable. First, as the king, I express my
gratitude.
\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Hah! How grateful!
MWP_SETTING SKIN Window2
MWP_VALID 16 1

That Rain, still a battle maniac as always. I
heard they took down three Igdras all by
themselves.
MWP_VALID 9 1

No way. That monster is so strong that even ten
soldiers wouldn't be enough...
MWP_VALID 16 1

As expected of \ANN[1]. It seems they took care of
it in an instant without changing their expression
this time too.
MWP_VALID 14 1

Hey, you know, Rain seems to be the female Holy
Knight Captain.
MWP_VALID 5 1

...No way. I can understand having those feelings
towards the Holy Knight Captain, but Rain?
MWP_VALID 14 1

I'm their classmate, but I was really surprised
because they didn't seem that cute...
MWP_VALID 5 1

But she's beautiful and has big breasts... I'm so
jealous...
MWP_INVALID

\N<Vice Holy Knight Commander>Hey, this is a
sacred place! Stop chatting!

\N<King>Rain, you are already an indispensable
existence in this country.

\N<King>Becoming a Holy Knight at such a young
age, achieving numerous accomplishments, and
possessing skills that can be compared to only a
few.

\N<King>I expect you to continue being the hope of
this country.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Yes! I will definitely meet
those expectations!
\N<King>I'm counting on you.
